1 AMEND House Bill No. 1825, Page 2, Section 50.333, Line 26, by deleting all of said line and
2 inserting in lieu thereof the following:
3
4 "In a county with more than one hundred fifty thousand but fewer than two hundred thousand
5 inhabitants, the prosecuting attorney and the sheriff shall be members of the salary commission.
6 In any county that utilizes assistant prosecuting attorneys, such assistant prosecuting attorneys
7 shall be members of the salary commission.
8 4. Members of the salary commission shall receive no additional compensation for their
9 services"; and
10
11 Further amend said bill and section, Pages 2-5, Lines 28-128, by renumbering subsequent
12 subsections accordingly; and
13
14 Further amend said bill by amending the title, enacting clause, and intersectional references
15 accordingly.
